claims:
16.一种电芯，其包括：16. A battery comprising:


         阴极极片，所述阴极极片包括阴极第一区和阴极第二区；a cathode pole piece, the cathode pole piece includes a cathode first region and a cathode second region;


         阳极极片，所述阳极极片包括阳极第一区和阳极第二区；an anode pole piece, the anode pole piece includes an anode first area and an anode second area;


         其中第一区的数值CB1为所述阳极第一区的单位面积容量CsA1与所述阴极第一区的单位面积容量CsC1的比值，The value CB 1 of the first area is the ratio of the capacity per unit area Cs A1 of the first area of the anode to the capacity Cs C1 per unit area of the first area of the cathode,


         其中第二区的数值CB2为所述阳极第二区的单位面积容量CsA2与所述阴极第二区的单位面积容量CsC2的比值，且wherein the value CB 2 of the second region is the ratio of the capacity per unit area Cs A2 of the second region of the anode to the capacity Cs C2 per unit area of the second region of the cathode, and


         其中CB2≥CB1。where CB 2 ≥CB 1 .
